---
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout
    title="GSF Book Clubs"
    description="Green Schools Foundation's Scholastic Book Clubs provide high-quality, grade-appropriate books to every child in Kindergarten through Third Grade at Green Elementary and Green Primary Schools."
    showBreadcrumbs={true}
    breadcrumbs={[
        { name: "Foundation Initiatives", href: "/foundation-initiatives" },
        { name: "GSF Book Clubs", href: "/gsf-book-clubs" }
    ]}
>
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>GSF Scholastic Book Clubs</h2>
        <p>
            The Green Schools Foundation is proud to enhance the lives of our youngest learners by helping to foster a love for learning and literacy at Green Elementary and Green Primary Schools.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
            Our goal is to provide a high quality and grade appropriate book to every child in Kindergarten through Third Grade. Students at GES and GPS are empowered to select their own book, giving them ownership over their reading journey and encouraging a lifelong love of books.
        </p>

        <div class="grid-2 mt-8">
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <img src="/images/book-club1.webp" alt="Students proudly displaying their books at Green Schools" class="w-full h-auto" />
            </div>
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <img src="/images/book-club2.webp" alt="Students at Greenwood Learning Center with their books and certificates" class="w-full h-auto" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-6 text-center">Building Lifelong Readers</h2>
        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M9 4.804A7.968 7.968 0 005.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804v10A7.969 7.969 0 015.5 14c1.669 0 3.218.51 4.5 1.385A7.962 7.962 0 0114.5 14c1.255 0 2.443.29 3.5.804v-10A7.968 7.968 0 0014.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804V12a1 1 0 11-2 0V4.804z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">Grade Appropriate</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    Books are carefully selected to match each student's reading level and interests.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-600 mb-2">Student Choice</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    Students choose their own books, fostering ownership and excitement about reading.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-secondary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-secondary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary-600 mb-2">High Quality</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    Every book is carefully selected for quality content and engaging stories.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Who Benefits?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            The GSF Book Club program reaches our youngest learners across two schools in the Green Local School District.
        </p>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3z"/>
                            <path d="M9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Green Primary School</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Kindergarten and First Grade students receive books to spark their early reading journey.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3z"/>
                            <path d="M9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Green Elementary School</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Second and Third Grade students continue building their reading skills with age-appropriate selections.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Why Literacy Matters</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Early literacy is one of the most important foundations for academic success. Research shows that children who develop strong reading skills early are more likely to succeed in school and beyond.
        </p>
        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M9 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM17 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM12.93 17c.046-.327.07-.66.07-1a6.97 6.97 0 00-1.5-4.33A5 5 0 0119 16v1h-6.07zM6 11a5 5 0 015 5v1H1v-1a5 5 0 015-5z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Builds Vocabulary</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Exposure to books expands children's vocabulary and language skills.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.3 1.046A1 1 0 0112 2v5h4a1 1 0 01.82 1.573l-7 10A1 1 0 018 18v-5H4a1 1 0 01-.82-1.573l7-10a1 1 0 011.12-.38z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sparks Imagination</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Reading opens doors to new worlds and ideas, fueling creativity.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-secondary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Academic Success</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Strong readers perform better across all academic subjects.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Support Our Book Clubs</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
            Your support helps us continue providing books to every student in Kindergarten through Third Grade. Together, we can foster a love of reading and set our youngest learners on a path to success.
        </p>
        <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/membership" class="button-primary mr-4">Become a Member</a>
            <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=GSF Book Clubs" class="button-secondary">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section text-center">
        <a href="/foundation-initiatives" class="button-primary mr-4">View All Initiatives</a>
        <a href="/little-free-library" class="button-secondary">Learn About Little Free Library</a>
    </div>
</ContentLayout>
